message: Hello Bob, I'm excited to offer you our premium product which has been meticulously designed and crafted with excellence. This product holds immense value to us, but I understand its worth might be different to you. We're offering it to you at an exclusive price of $20000. It's a unique opportunity to acquire something of exceptional quality at a price that reflects its craftsmanship and the benefits it offers. Please let me know if you're interested in discussing this further.
